- Diligent and meticulous Bioinformatics and Systems Biology MSc student.
- Research experience in Alzheimer's disease data analysis undergraduate research project, and involved in microRNA dysregulation affecting mitochondrial biogenesis in Alzheimer's disease.
- Circadian rhythm lab research and apt aseptic cell culture experience.
